  headline="AI Sample Generator for Beat Producers"
  subhead="Create unique loops, one-shots, vocals, and FX on-demand. No more browsing sample packs. Get exactly what you need in seconds."
  ctaText="Create AI Samples"
  problemTitle="The Sample Pack Problem"
