  solutionTitle="AI-Generated Samples On-Demand"
  solutionDescription="Describe the sample you need and get it in seconds. Every loop, one-shot, and vocal sample is AI-generated and unique. No shared libraries, no overused sounds. Build beats with original samples that match your exact vision. Full commercial rights, stem export included."
